    > 以备不时之需。<a
      href="https://post.knowsex.net/archives/how-to-visit-again"
      >了解如何再度访问...</a
    >
  </p>
  <div id="domain-notice"></div>
  <div class="browser_tip"></div>
  {
    language == "zh-tw" && (
      <p class="bg-light tip-bar">
        <span class="darkmode-ignore">ℹ️</span>{" "}
        本页面由自动化程序从简体中文转换而来，如发现错误，欢迎
        <a href="/general/communicate">报告给我们</a>。
      </p>
    )
  }
  <br />
  <div style="color:grey; font-size:.8em;">构建日期 {date}</div>
  <Card
    href="main/human-reproductive-system"
    bgID="no1"
    title="人类生殖系统"
    enTitle="Human Reproductive System"
  />
  <Card
    href="main/puberty-and-adolescence"
    bgID="pa-bg"
    title="青春期"
    enTitle="Puberty and Adolescence"
  />
  <Card
    href="main/menstrual-cycle"
    bgID="menstrual-cycle"
    title="月经周期"
    enTitle="Menstrual Cycle"
  />
  <Card
    href="main/sexual-activity"
    bgID="no2"
    title="性行为"
    enTitle="Sexual Activity"
  />
  <Card
    href="main/sexual-physiology"
    bgID="sp-bg"
